  h2 What is Graph Director?
  p 
  | Graph director visualizes the IMDb ratings of various directors over time. <br />
  | Movies are plotted on a graph, by release year and by rating. <br />
  | This site was heavily influenced by 
  a(href='http://graphtv.kevinformatics.com') graphtv
  | .

  h2 Why don't all directors / movies appear?
  p Only movies with at least 10,000 votes were considered. Moreover, only directors having at least 3 such movies were included.

